## PROMPT 4 — Generate a Dashboard / Homepage

```
Generate a dashboard homepage for the mashup at <project-path>.

Layout:
- Use soho-homepage as the container.
- Include the following widgets:
  - <e.g. A KPI card (soho-card) showing total orders>
  - <e.g. A bar chart (soho-bar) showing orders by month>
  - <e.g. A listview (soho-listview) showing recent activity>

For each widget:
1. Read the corresponding .d.ts in Mashup Manager/Components Library/ids-enterprise-ng/lib/<component>/
2. Read the example HTML in Mashup Manager/Components Library/scraped_components/<slug>/example-index_html/page.html

Use mock/static data for now unless otherwise specified.
Follow all rules in .cursor/rules/.
```

